### R Plumber GLMM local smoke
GET http://localhost:8000/healthz

### Fit small GLMM
POST http://localhost:8000/glmm/fit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "observations": [
    {"student_id": "s1", "item_id": "i1", "correct": 1},
    {"student_id": "s1", "item_id": "i2", "correct": 0},
    {"student_id": "s2", "item_id": "i1", "correct": 1},
    {"student_id": "s2", "item_id": "i2", "correct": 1}
  ]
}

### Predict with compact model
POST http://localhost:8000/glmm/predict
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "model": {
    "fixed_effects": {"(Intercept)": 0},
    "ranef": {"student_id": [], "item_id": []}
  },
  "newdata": [{"student_id": "s1", "item_id": "i1"}]
}

### Forecast summary
POST http://localhost:8000/forecast/summary
Content-Type: application/json

{"mean": 0.1, "sd": 0.5, "target": 0.0}
